{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found one subtle issue while reviewing the new planner: regex-based splits can carry trailing whitespace, which would skew the stored source offsets. I\u2019m tightening that now so the persisted text slice and the recorded start/end offset...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_112", "text": "I found one subtle issue while reviewing the new planner: regex-based splits can carry trailing whitespace, which would skew the stored source offsets. I\u2019m tightening that now so the persisted text slice and the recorded start/end offsets always describe the same exact substring.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 228, "prompt_index": 73, "prompt_name": "72 \u2014 Narration Segmentation Strategy", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T14:38:55-07:00"}
