{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented durable narration segmentation and committed the production changes in `2cc0458` (`feat(prompt-72): narration segmentation`). The backend now creates a persisted `narration_segments` plan for each audio job, stores exact manu...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_139", "text": "Implemented durable narration segmentation and committed the production changes in `2cc0458` (`feat(prompt-72): narration segmentation`). The backend now creates a persisted `narration_segments` plan for each audio job, stores exact manuscript offsets and pause/music hints, and exposes `total_segments` through hydration/realtime so audio work can resume segment by segment.\n\nVerification completed: backend pytest passes (`47` targeted tests, plus `67` session/API tests), `ruff check` passes, frontend Vitest passes (`108` tests total), and `npm run build` passes. No browser/screenshot QA was run because this did not change rendered UI behavior. The required reviewer summary was written to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/72_narration_segmentation_strategy/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 276, "prompt_index": 73, "prompt_name": "72 \u2014 Narration Segmentation Strategy", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T14:42:43-07:00"}
